data.description: Charming 2 owner home, 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths. Master-tray ceiling, ceiling fan, walk-in closet, hardwood floors, master full bath. Spacious Living room with vaulted ceiling, ceiling fan, spectacular window, hardwood flooring, fireplace does not convey, spacious kitchen - with many cabinets, deep sink, built in area for computer on desk, backsplash, granite counters, hardwood floors, canned lighting. All appliances stay, Great Sunroom that is 227 sq ft. - tile flooring, windows with screens, 2 ceiling fans, heat & ac.  Nice patio in back with fenced yard, swing stays in concrete. The crawl has been B-dried by previous owner-warranty to convey. Heat & Ac - 3 yrs old 10 yr warranty to passed on. This is a must see! You will fall in love with this home and area. This home is priced to sell under appraisal from 1/23.
